OL,3,CGovernment to make #6bn welfare
OL,4,Csavings with benefits shake-up
OL,6,FEven those with extreme disabilities
OL,7,Fin the unfit to work category are
OL,8,Flikely to lose money under new
OL,9,Fgovernment plans, ITV News Deputy
OL,10,FPolitical Editor, Anushka Asthana
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FThe government is planning to unveil
OL,14,Fmore than #6bn of welfare savings that
OL,15,Fwill see far tougher tests imposed for
OL,16,Fa key disability benefit, some
OL,17,Fpayments frozen in 2026, and major
OL,18,Fchanges to the way universal credit is
OL,19,Fcalculated, ITV News can reveal.
