OL,3,CGovernment to make #6bn welfare
OL,4,Csavings with benefits shake-up
OL,6,FThe aim of the measures is to
OL,7,Fmassively increase the incentives for
OL,8,Fpeople to remain in the work-search
OL,9,Fcategory of Universal Credit, even if
OL,10,Fthey suffer with a health condition or
OL,11,Fdisability, but also to more than #6bn
OL,12,Fa year by the end of the decade.
OL,14,FEarlier this week I reported a number
OL,15,Fof senior sources across government
OL,16,Ftold me they have been asked to
OL,17,Fidentify the 20% of spending within
OL,18,Ftheir departments that they see as
OL,19,Flowest priority.
