OL,4,Csavings with benefits shake-up
OL,6,FOne suggested that they had been asked
OL,7,Fto go even further - up to 40%.
OL,9,FRachel Reeves and Liz Kendall will
OL,10,Fargue that many people with
OL,11,Fdisabilities are desperate to work but
OL,12,Fsimply don't have adequate support to
OL,13,Ffind the right job, but with the move
OL,14,Fresulting in significant cuts to
OL,15,Fbenefits for some of the most
OL,16,Fvulnerable, it will be hugely
OL,17,Fcontroversial.
