OL,4,Csavings with benefits shake-up
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV News last
OL,7,Fmonth, the Work and Pensions Secretary
OL,8,Ftold me too many people are "taking
OL,9,Fthe mickey" by claiming benefits when
OL,10,Fthey should be working.
OL,12,FLiz Kendall said the number of people
OL,13,Fon benefits who pretend they can't
OL,14,Fwork is "not good enough," and "we
OL,15,Fhave to end that".
