OL,3,CGovernment to make #6bn welfare
OL,4,Csavings with benefits shake-up
OL,6,FUnder these plans - even those with
OL,7,Fextreme disabilities in the unfit to
OL,8,Fwork category are likely to lose
OL,9,Fmoney. Meanwhile many will be taken
OL,10,Fout of PIP payments which are not
OL,11,Flinked to work at all- but are there
OL,12,Fto help with the additional cost of
OL,13,Fdisabilities.
OL,15,FJames Taylor, Executive Director of
OL,16,Fstrategy at disability equality
OL,17,Fcharity Scope said: "Ripping PIP away
OL,18,Fwill be catastrophic for disabled
OL,19,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
