OL,4,Csavings with benefits shake-up
OL,6,F"Making the wrong choice will have a
OL,7,Fdevastating impact on disabled people
OL,8,Fand their families."
OL,10,FLaura Thomas, Head of Policy at the MS
OL,11,FSociety, says: "We're deeply concerned
OL,12,Fat the suggestion of welfare cuts and
OL,13,Furge the government not to take such a
OL,14,Fcruel and harmful approach.
OL,16,F"People with MS have told us they've
OL,17,Fbeen filled with worry in recent weeks
OL,18,Fabout what these changes could mean
OL,19,Ffor them.
