OL,4,Csavings with benefits shake-up
OL,6,F"MS can be debilitating, exhausting
OL,7,Fand unpredictable. And we know that
OL,8,Falready too many people with the
OL,9,Fcondition are struggling to pay for
OL,10,Fessentials like food and medications
OL,11,Fwith the benefits they do receive.
OL,13,F"So any cuts will inevitably increase
OL,14,Fpoverty and destitution, and worsen
OL,15,Fhealth, amongst a community who are
OL,16,Falready likely to be struggling."
